udig tussen warm & wit licht, brengt sfeer in elke ruimte.<\/p><p><strong>Dimbaar:<\/strong> Kies tussen 3 opties van zacht tot fel licht, eenvoudig met Touch-bediening<\/p><p><strong>Duurzaam Materiaal:<\/strong> De lamp gaat lang mee dankzij het hoogwaardige metaal.<\/p><p><strong>Draadloos:<\/strong> Voeg overal licht toe, zonder gedoe met kabels.<\/p>","text_style":"body"}}},"block_order":["caption_MeYD8U","heading_JLkj7e","9bd8fb44-fa40-449d-be77-8f37af118496"],"settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/gif_2_50424d90-f982-49f3-9978-e3fd7ae6da8e.webp","height":"adapt","color_scheme":"background-1","section_color_scheme":"background-1","content_layout":"no-overlap","layout":"text_first","desktop_content_position":"top","desktop_content_alignment":"left","mobile_content_alignment":"left"}},"2cb68c65-93ce-4030-a625-5bac24b42fe4":{"type":"image-with-text","blocks":{"caption_W9Mt9x":{"type":"caption","settings":{"caption":"SUSTAINABILITY","text_style":"caption-with-letter-spacing","text_size":"medium"}},"heading_gGLCbq":{"type":"heading","settings":{"heading_size":"h1"}},"f1d0c312-6e0a-443f-a521-b731697ad34f":{"type":"text","settings":{"text":"<p>De Luminate Tafellamp gebruikt zuinige<strong> <\/strong>LED-lampen, waardoor je <strong>geld bespaart<\/strong> op energiekosten en je steentje bijdraagt aan het milieu.<\/p>","text_style":"body"}}},"block_order":["caption_W9Mt9x","heading_gGLCbq","f1d0c312-6e0a-443f-a521-b731697ad34f"],"settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/5_cfabdbfe-307a-42d2-b90f-6aac655326a5.webp","height":"adapt","color_scheme":"background-1","section_color_scheme":"background-1","content_layout":"no-overlap","layout":"image_first","desktop_content_position":"top","desktop_content_alignment":"left","mobile_content_alignment":"left"}},"9f8ed1f4-75b8-4974-842c-754126d14d2b":{"type":"image-with-text","blocks":{"caption_CxKtjU":{"type":"caption","settings":{"caption":"DESIGN","text_style":"subtitle","text_size":"medium"}},"heading_HzfMpD":{"typ